metadata.name: TAROT Presents Imaginary Friend
metadata.description:
"I see your drinking 1%. Does that mean you think you're fat? Cause you're not. You could be drinking whole if you wanted to."

Wrote a song about getting bread crumbed & directed/edited this video in homage to the early 2000s classic film introduction credits.

A Visualizer by Gusteau's Productions:
Directer/Editor:Jordyn Benedict
ADs: Layton Lupone & Gretchen MacIlwaine

Music written by Jordyn Benedict & Luke Saison
Produced by Blake Burchette & Tate Gardner
Mixed by Blake Burchette
Mastered by Adam Grover at Sterling Sound
Performed by TAROT

The holder of this NFT will land a spot on the Tarotsings Soul Tribe and gets an exclusive inside peek of the album and choose one song to get a music video!
